commit.message:
rs6000.h (ASM_OUTPUT_OPTIONS): Delete.

	* rs6000/rs6000.h (ASM_OUTPUT_OPTIONS): Delete.
	(ASM_COMMENT_START): Define.
	(ASM_FILE_START): Delete option output support.

From-SVN: r11999
